column5: Do you need a manual? Lost yours?...Need a part number? Check this site out...Must have every TM made by Minkota or MotorGuide!+ reels, electronics and yama o/b... Helped me and hopefully it can help you!   http://www.nuggetfishing.com.au/index.php?option=com_vfm&Itemid=412  http://www.nuggetfishing.com.au/index.php?option=com_vfm&Itemid=412&dir=Fishing+Reels  http://www.nuggetfishing.com.au/index.php?option=com_vfm&Itemid=412&dir=Electric+Motors|Minn+Kota  http://www.nuggetfishing.com.au/index.php?option=com_vfm&Itemid=412&dir=Electric+Motors|Motorguide  http://www.nuggetfishing.com.au/index.php?option=com_vfm&Itemid=412&dir=Marine+Electronics
Nice find IronHorse! I even found the schematic for my Abu 503. If it falls apart it's going in the garbage though hahaha. Sometimes I like when things break... it means it's time for a NEW one!
